{"thig10.1:0.1":"Therigatha 10.1 ","thig10.1:0.2":"Ekadasakanipata ","thig10.1:0.3":"Kisagotamitherigatha ","thig10.1:1.1":"“Kalyanamittata munina, ","thig10.1:1.2":"lokam adissa vannita; ","thig10.1:1.3":"Kalyanamitte bhajamano, ","thig10.1:1.4":"api balo pandito assa. ","thig10.1:2.1":"Bhajitabba sappurisa, ","thig10.1:2.2":"Panna tatha vaddhati bhajantanam; ","thig10.1:2.3":"Bhajamano sappurise, ","thig10.1:2.4":"Sabbehipi dukkhehi pamucceyya. ","thig10.1:3.1":"Dukkhanca vijaneyya, ","thig10.1:3.2":"Dukkhassa ca samudayam nirodham; ","thig10.1:3.3":"Atthangikanca maggam, ","thig10.1:3.4":"Cattaripi ariyasaccani”. ","thig10.1:4.1":"“Dukkho itthibhavo, ","thig10.1:4.2":"Akkhato purisadammasarathina; ","thig10.1:4.3":"Sapattikampi hi dukkham, ","thig10.1:4.4":"Appekacca sakim vijatayo. ","thig10.1:5.1":"Galake api kantanti, ","thig10.1:5.2":"Sukhumaliniyo visani khadanti; ","thig10.1:5.3":"Janamarakamajjhagata, ","thig10.1:5.4":"Ubhopi byasanani anubhonti”. ","thig10.1:6.1":"“Upavijanna gacchanti, ","thig10.1:6.2":"addasaham patim matam; ","thig10.1:6.3":"Panthamhi vijayitvana, ","thig10.1:6.4":"appattava sakam gharam. ","thig10.1:7.1":"Dve putta kalakata, ","thig10.1:7.2":"Pati ca panthe mato kapanikaya; ","thig10.1:7.3":"Mata pita ca bhata, ","thig10.1:7.4":"Dayhanti ca ekacitakayam”. ","thig10.1:8.1":"“Khinakuline kapane, ","thig10.1:8.2":"Anubhutam te dukham aparimanam; ","thig10.1:8.3":"Assu ca te pavattam, ","thig10.1:8.4":"Bahuni ca jatisahassani. ","thig10.1:9.1":"Vasita susanamajjhe, ","thig10.1:9.2":"Athopi khaditani puttamamsani; ","thig10.1:9.3":"Hatakulika sabbagarahita, ","thig10.1:9.4":"Matapatika amatamadhigacchim. ","thig10.1:10.1":"Bhavito me maggo, ","thig10.1:10.2":"Ariyo atthangiko amatagami; ","thig10.1:10.3":"Nibbanam sacchikatam, ","thig10.1:10.4":"Dhammadasam avekkhimham. ","thig10.1:11.1":"Ahamamhi kantasalla, ","thig10.1:11.2":"Ohitabhara katanhi karaniyam; ","thig10.1:11.3":"Kisa gotami theri, ","thig10.1:11.4":"Vimuttacitta imam bhani”ti. ","thig10.1:12.1":"… Kisa gotami theri …. ","thig10.1:13.1":"Ekadasakanipato nitthito. "}